SUB_W06_WRLD_DIVA_000_CUT_000_000.text:
This world is known as the Kosmos;
I imagine one could say each living
being is a universe unto itself.

SUB_W06_EVAR_DIVA_FIRST_CONTACT_000_CUT_.text:
Oh dear, this is a proper mess;
I dinnae even understand enough
about myself to argue with ye!

SUB_W06_EVAR_DIVA_HEART_010_CUT_020_060.text:
In that case, I'm coming with ye;
more malignancies could strike at
any moment, and ye'll need the help.
